      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The power is managed by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and delivered to the tarmac via a factory M Variable Differential Lock. Technical upkeep is current, including critical double VANOS service and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension geometry remains true, offering the communicative steering and balanced chassis dynamics that define this generation. A mechanically sound, analog performance machine ready for the open road.",
